{"tid":1469420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有問題既唔係打人，而係塞通道。我哋係要人，係非常唔夠人","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:17:39.000Z","uid":249395,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef39d404b838d26d6043e79a219fbbc8aa302ea4","tid":1469420,"uid":249395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:47:07.000Z","msg":"大家放錯重點係打人<br />\n我哋宜家赢在多人圍堵機場T1位置<br />\n琴日唔夠人而走左去塞離境通道<br />\n我地目前為止未輸，只係形式唔係塞通道<br />\n<br />\n重申<br />\n機場活動<br />\n不衝擊<br />\n不被捕"},{"pid":"afc839586ce1ed2c41cca8ac1af4d08410e35121","tid":1469420,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:49:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b84bcd1c66f69422b166fd5a583fa687aee82d","tid":1469420,"uid":249395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:58:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3af2c398d49e740c52e7599c77247781c316a83a","tid":1469420,"uid":249395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}